**/outputs/*.csv
**/outputs/*.json
**/outputs/*.html
**/outputs/data/*.csv
**/outputs/data/*.json

# 凭证防御性规则（当前不在仓库内，但防止误拷入）
*.pem
*.p12
*.key
**/service_account*.json
**/application_default_credentials.json
.env
.env.*
.lark-cli/
.gcloud/
